<br>
More than one language in EverQuest has a different name in the skill list (what you see when you go to train at your guild-hall) than in the list you get when you type /language help.<br>
<br>
-Human Tongue is Common (only on this server)<br>
-Combine used to also be Giant, but Vernat changed it<br>
-Elder Teir'Dal is Kobold (go figure)<br>
-Vah Shir is &quot;&quot; (blank) in the skill list<br>
-Teir'Dal is Dark Elvish (this one makes sense)<br>
