Humans start with Human only<br>
Erudites start with Erudite and some Human<br>
Barbarians start with Barbarian and some Human<br>
Gnomes start with Gnome and some Dwarf<br>
Dwarves start with Dwarf and some Gnome<br>
High Elves start with Elf and some Elder Elf<br>
Dark Elves start with Dark Elf and some Elder Elf<br>
Half Elves start with FULL Elf and FULL Human, regardless of starting city.<br>
<br>
Rogues also start with Thieves' Cant.<br>
Please fill in the gaps.  I don't believe any corrections are needed, but there are some races I just don't know about.<br>
